data.description: Wonderful family home located in a desirable Troy neighborhood. This brick ranch with a full basement boasts lots of space for its new family. Many updates have been completed including newer windows, roof and air conditioning unit. The large eat in kitchen has plenty of counter space including an island and room for entertaining. The great room has a beautiful fireplace (with electric logs) with built in shelving on both sides. The master bathroom has an attached bathroom which is currently housing the washer and dryer but could easily be converted back to a full bath by relocating the washer and dryer to the laundry room in the basement! Two additional bedrooms and a full bath make this home perfect for the new owner! The full basement provides added space for entertaining or storage and is partially finished! Pool Table remains!
